<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .failure-details {
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .failure-details h3 {
            color: #333333;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .failure-details table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .failure-details td {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .failure-details td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .failure-details td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .reason {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .suggestions {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .suggestions h3 {
            color: #333333;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .suggestions ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .suggestions li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .suggestions li:before {
            content: "\2022";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #e0e0e0, transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>&#10007; Payment Failed</h1>
            <p>We couldn't process your payment</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="message">
                <p>Hi there,</p>
                <p>Unfortunately, the payment for order <span class="highlight">#<%= orderId %></span> could not be processed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="failure-details">
                <h3>Payment Details</h3>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Order ID</td>
                        <td>#<%= orderId %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Status</td>
                        <td><span class="highlight">Failed</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Reason</td>
                        <td><span class="reason"><%= reason %></span></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="suggestions">
                <h3>What you can do</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Check that your card details are correct</li>
                    <li>Ensure you have sufficient funds</li>
                    <li>Try a different payment method</li>
                    <li>Contact your bank if the issue persists</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">Retry Payment</a>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Contact our support team anytime.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
